---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Main.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="max-w-[660px] mx-auto px-[var(--container-padding)]">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <section class="pt-[4rem] pb-[3rem]">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="text-[var(--color-description)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors"
        >
          ← Back to Portfolio
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-[3rem] font-semibold leading-tight mb-4">
            Alfa Bank - Alfa Travel
          </h1>
          <p class="text-[1.25rem] text-[var(--color-description)] mb-6">
            2023–2025
          </p>
          <p>
            Alfa-Bank is Russia's largest private bank, providing financial
            services to over 22 million customers through 672+ branches
            nationwide. As a universal bank, it offers comprehensive banking
            operations including retail, corporate banking, investment services,
            and digital solutions with approximately 25,000 employees.
          </p>
          <p>
            Alfa Travel is the bank's integrated travel booking platform,
            providing comprehensive travel services including flights, hotels,
            train tickets, and vacation packages. The platform leverages the
            bank's ecosystem approach, allowing customers to utilize bonus
            points and rewards across all banking services while seamlessly
            booking and paying for travel through their existing banking
            relationship.
          </p>
          <h2>My Role</h2>
          <p>
            Served as the sole designer within the travel services department,
            responsible for designing and enhancing the comprehensive travel
            booking platform. Working within Alfa Bank's established design
            system, I leveraged the bank's component library to create cohesive
            user experiences across flight bookings, hotel reservations, train
            tickets, and vacation packages while ensuring seamless integration
            with the broader banking ecosystem and rewards program.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main></Layout
>
